Penelope，你有沒有想過
Penelope, did you, did you ever think

585
00:36:06,498 --> 00:36:08,238
去看另一位精神科醫生？
of going to another psychiatrist?

586
00:36:09,209 --> 00:36:11,791
不，那樣不忠誠。
No, that would be disloyal.

587
00:36:13,129 --> 00:36:14,494
我一點也幫不了你。
I'm not helping you at all.

588
00:36:15,632 --> 00:36:17,714
當然你幫了。
Of course you are.

589
00:36:17,801 --> 00:36:20,383
Gregory，對不起。我會把錢包寄回去。
Gregory, I'm sorry. I'll send the wallet back.

590
00:36:20,470 --> 00:36:22,210
不止是這個。
It's not only this.

591
00:36:23,306 --> 00:36:26,719
哦，別因爲我搶了家銀行就氣餒。
Oh, don't be discouraged just because I stuck up a bank.

592
00:36:26,810 --> 00:36:28,391
是你丈夫的銀行。
Your husband's bank.

593
00:36:28,478 --> 00:36:30,309
是的，James 的銀行。
Yeah, James' bank.

594
00:36:30,397 --> 00:36:32,934
爲什麼是他那家銀行？爲什麼不是別人的？
Why his bank? Why not somebody else's bank?

595
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:35,391
你爲什麼用左手寫字？
Why are you writing left-handed?

596
00:36:37,278 --> 00:36:39,564
我是事後幫助掩護的人。
I'm being an accessory after the fact.

597
00:36:44,452 --> 00:36:46,363
你介意替我舔一下這個嗎？
Would you mind licking this for me?

598
00:36:47,831 --> 00:36:49,162
我太乾了。
I'm too dry.

599
00:36:53,461 --> 00:36:56,043
你當初怎麼會嫁給那樣的男人？
Whatever made you marry a man like that in the first place?

600
00:36:57,006 --> 00:37:00,590
哦，James 起初並不是那種男人。
Oh, James wasn't a man like that in the first place.

601
00:37:00,677 --> 00:37:02,008
哦，不。
Oh, no.

602
00:37:02,679 --> 00:37:05,762
我第一次遇到 James 是在格林威治村的一個酒窖裏
The first time I met James was at a Greenwich village cellar

603
00:37:05,849 --> 00:37:07,840
叫做 Plush Pig。
known as the plush pig.

604
00:37:07,934 --> 00:37:09,765
我在那裏工作了幾個月。
I'd been working there a couple of months.

605
00:37:09,853 --> 00:37:11,844
那是我在紐約的第一份正經工作。
It was my first real job in New York.

