<i>♪ 給我翅膀幫助我飛翔 ♪</i>
<i>♪ give me wings and help me fly ♪</i>

612
00:37:45,597 --> 00:37:49,089
<i>♪ 但沒有你無論晝夜 ♪</i>
<i>♪ but without you night and day ♪</i>

