<i>♪ 太陽也變得灰暗 ♪</i>
<i>♪ the sun is gray ♪</i>

615
00:37:58,860 --> 00:38:02,603
<i>♪ 你掛起月亮 ♪</i>
<i>♪ you hang the moon ♪</i>

616
00:38:02,697 --> 00:38:09,193
<i>♪ 在天空中撒滿星辰 ♪</i>
<i>♪ scatter stars throughout the sky ♪</i>

617
00:38:09,287 --> 00:38:14,247
<i>♪ 我內心所有的美好 ♪</i>
<i>♪ all of the good things within me ♪</i>

618
00:38:14,334 --> 00:38:19,829
<i>♪ 都必須透過你的眼來見證 ♪</i>
<i>♪ must first be seen through your eye ♪</i>

619
00:38:23,092 --> 00:38:27,756
<i>♪ 只有一件事是錯的 ♪</i>
<i>♪ there is only one thing wrong ♪</i>

620
00:38:28,932 --> 00:38:33,596
<i>♪ 太陽是灰色的 ♪</i>
<i>♪ the sun is gray ♪</i>

621
00:38:34,646 --> 00:38:40,858
<i>♪ 太陽是灰色的 ♪</i>
<i>♪ the sun is gray ♪</i>

622
00:38:59,420 --> 00:39:01,661
魔鬼的小提琴在說話。
The devil's fiddle speaks.

623
00:39:35,415 --> 00:39:36,655
嗨。
Hi.

624
00:39:37,375 --> 00:39:40,617
- 嗯。Penelope Gordon 小姐？ - 嗯哼。
- Huh. Miss Penelope Gordon? - Mm-hm.

625
00:39:40,712 --> 00:39:43,545
如果你坐下，就不用彎着腰了。
If you sit down, you won't have to scrunch over.

626
00:39:43,631 --> 00:39:46,748
我可以請你喝一杯，但只有水。
I'd offer you a drink, but it's only water.

627
00:39:46,843 --> 00:39:48,799
你介意我把眼睛取出來嗎？
Would you excuse me while I take out my eyes?

628
00:39:55,018 --> 00:39:59,762
我是 James Elcott，市聯邦銀行。
I'm James Elcott, city federal bank.

629
00:39:59,856 --> 00:40:02,063
嗯，隱形眼鏡。
Hm, contacts.

630
00:40:02,150 --> 00:40:03,731
哦，現在我能看得更清楚你了。
Oh, now I can see you much better.

631
00:40:08,448 --> 00:40:10,359
好吧，我從沒和銀行握過手。
Well, I never shook hands with a bank before.

632
00:40:12,410 --> 00:40:14,696
Penelope Gordon 小姐，我怎麼沒收到你的來信？
How is it I haven't heard from you, miss Gordon?

633
00:40:14,787 --> 00:40:17,073
嗯，可能是因爲我們剛認識不久。
Well, it's probably because we've only just met.

634
00:40:17,165 --> 00:40:19,747
但在過去兩個月我給你寫了九封信。
But I've written you nine times in the last two months.

635
00:40:19,834 --> 00:40:22,450
哦，你真喜歡民謠，是嗎？
Oh, you really love folk songs, do you?

636
00:40:22,545 --> 00:40:25,207
並不完全是。不，這事是公務。
Not exactly. No, this is business.

637
00:40:25,298 --> 00:40:28,540
市聯邦接受了一個小遺產的受託管理
City federal has accepted trusteeship of a modest estate

638
00:40:28,635 --> 00:40:30,250
是你母親的表親留給你的。
left to you by your mother's cousin.

639
00:40:30,345 --> 00:40:32,506
你確定是對的 Penelope Gordon 嗎？
Are you sure you've got the right Penelope Gordon?

640
00:40:32,597 --> 00:40:33,597
絕對。
Absolutely.

641
00:40:33,681 --> 00:40:35,281
遺產的收入不會很多，
The income from the estate won't be much,

642
00:40:35,350 --> 00:40:36,635
但有些文件需要簽字。
but there are papers to sign.

643
00:40:36,726 --> 00:40:39,468
你真的從未收到過我的任何信嗎？
You're certain you never received any of my letters?

644
00:40:39,562 --> 00:40:41,974
啊，我知道怎麼回事了。
Ah, I know what happened.

645
00:40:42,065 --> 00:40:44,898
你看，我從不打開我的郵件。
You see, I never open my mail.

646
00:40:44,984 --> 00:40:46,520
哦，誰替你打開？
Oh, who does it for you?

647
00:40:46,611 --> 00:40:48,727
- 沒有人。 - 那郵件都去哪兒了？
- Nobody. - What happens to it?

648
00:40:48,821 --> 00:40:51,984
通常我把它塞進抽屜裏某處，
Well, usually, I stick it away in a drawer someplace

649
00:40:52,075 --> 00:40:55,693
然後總是忘了或丟了。
and then I always forget it or it gets lost.

650
00:40:56,287 --> 00:40:58,323
你不會因此失去很多朋友嗎？
Don't you lose a lot of friends that way?

651
00:40:58,414 --> 00:41:00,996
哦，不，正好相反。
Oh, no, just the opposite.

652
00:41:01,084 --> 00:41:03,996
你看，如果你寫信給我而我回信，
You see, if you write me a letter and I answer it,

653
00:41:04,087 --> 00:41:05,668
那你就得回我信。
then you have to answer mine.

654
00:41:05,755 --> 00:41:08,108
然後我回答你的第二封，你得寫第三封
Then I answer your second letter and you have to write me a third

655
00:41:08,132 --> 00:41:09,247
並回答我的第二封。
and answer to my second.

656
00:41:09,342 --> 00:41:10,569
然後我得寫第三封，
And then I have to write you a third

657
00:41:10,593 --> 00:41:11,924
你得寄第四封。
and you have to send me a fourth.

658
00:41:12,011 --> 00:41:14,365
很快，我們忙着互相寫信，
And pretty soon, we're so busy writing letters to each other

659
00:41:14,389 --> 00:41:16,175
就沒時間做朋友了。
we haven't got time to be friends.

660
00:41:18,393 --> 00:41:20,054
是嗎？
Isn't that true?

661
00:41:20,144 --> 00:41:24,683
嗯，我從沒這麼想過，嗯。
Uh, I-i-I never, I never thought of it like that, hm.

662
00:41:24,774 --> 00:41:27,231
無論如何，我可以回家再找找你的信。
Well, anyway, I-I could still look for your letters at home.

663
00:41:27,318 --> 00:41:28,318
那有幫助嗎？
Would that help?

664
00:41:28,403 --> 00:41:30,644
嗯，我們應該討論這些，是的。
Well, we ought to discuss them, yes.

665
00:41:32,323 --> 00:41:34,063
哦，親愛的。
Oh, dear.

666
00:41:34,158 --> 00:41:35,523
怎麼了？
What is it?

667
00:41:35,618 --> 00:41:38,280
我把隱形眼鏡掉了。我總是弄丟它們。
I've dropped my contact lens. I'm always losing them.

668
00:41:38,371 --> 00:41:39,736
哦，別把褲子弄髒。
Oh, oh, don't get your pants dirty.

669
00:41:39,831 --> 00:41:41,742
哦，沒事的。
Oh, that's alright.

670
00:41:41,833 --> 00:41:44,495
你、嗯，你覺得我們可以、呃，
Do you, um, do you think we could, uh,

671
00:41:44,585 --> 00:41:46,746
明天找個時間見面嗎？
get together sometime tomorrow?

672
00:41:46,838 --> 00:41:48,749
哦，當然，吃個晚飯怎麼樣？
Oh, sure, how about dinner?

673
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,751
我——我要請些朋友來。
I-I'm gonna have some friends in.

674
00:41:50,842 --> 00:41:53,754
呃，那太好了。
Uh, that's wonderful.

675
00:41:53,845 --> 00:41:56,632
哦，這些隱形眼鏡，真小。
Oh, these contacts, they're so tiny.

676
00:41:56,723 --> 00:41:58,259
我們怎麼可能找到它們呢。
We're never going to find them.

677
00:41:58,349 --> 00:41:59,555
那，有關係嗎？
Well, does it matter?

678
00:41:59,642 --> 00:42:01,758
你自己不是說過不用它們看得更清楚嗎。
You said yourself, you can see better without them.

679
00:42:01,853 --> 00:42:03,389
哦，清楚多了。
Oh, much better.

680
00:42:03,479 --> 00:42:04,969
我想以前和我約會的那位驗光師
I think this optometrist I was dating

681
00:42:05,064 --> 00:42:06,770
給了我錯的處方。
gave me the wrong prescription.

682
00:42:06,858 --> 00:42:09,395
我能問你件事嗎？
May I ask something?

683
00:42:10,695 --> 00:42:12,401
你爲什麼戴它們？
Why do you wear them?

684
00:42:12,488 --> 00:42:14,695
嗯，他說它們能讓我的眼睛顯得有神采。
Well, he said they make my eyes look luminous.

685
00:42:16,159 --> 00:42:18,070
我覺得我的眼睛本來就很有神采了。
I think they're luminous already.

686
00:42:19,871 --> 00:42:21,236
而且也挺漂亮的。
And quite beautiful.

687
00:42:23,374 --> 00:42:27,413
哦，那好，那麼我就不用戴隱形眼鏡了，是嗎？
Oh, well, then I don't need to wear the contacts, do I?

688
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:32,501
我很高興你來看我。
I'm glad you came to see me.

689
00:42:34,135 --> 00:42:35,796
我也是。
So am I.

690
00:42:35,887 --> 00:42:37,843
我很期待明晚。
I'm looking forward to tomorrow night.

691
00:42:38,431 --> 00:42:39,762
我也是。
So am I.

692
00:42:46,731 --> 00:42:48,892
現在我想起來了，可以請你站起來嗎？
And now I'd like to get up, please.

693
00:42:48,983 --> 00:42:50,018
什麼？
Pardon?

694
00:42:50,109 --> 00:42:52,270
你跪在我的頭髮上了。
You're kneeling on my hair.

695
00:42:52,361 --> 00:42:54,241
- 哦，我太... - 哦，小心那個...
- Oh, I'm terribly... - Oh, watch out for the...

696
00:42:56,783 --> 00:42:57,898
菸斗。
Pipe.

697
00:42:58,993 --> 00:43:00,824
哦，天哪。哦。
Oh, dear. Oh.

698
00:43:00,912 --> 00:43:03,824
真是非常抱歉。
I'm terribly sorry.

699
00:43:03,915 --> 00:43:04,915
你還好嗎？
A-are you alright?

700
00:43:04,999 --> 00:43:06,990
沒事，完全沒事。
It's alright. Quite alright.

701
00:43:07,085 --> 00:43:09,246
沒什麼好擔心的。
There's nothing to concern yourself about.

702
00:43:11,714 --> 00:43:12,714
哎呀。
Oh, dear.

703
00:43:15,134 --> 00:43:18,547
哦，你找到了我的隱形眼鏡。
Oh, you found my contact lens.

704
00:43:40,868 --> 00:43:42,199
嗯？
Yeah?

705
00:43:44,580 --> 00:43:46,070
Penelope Gordon 小姐？
Miss Penelope Gordon?

706
00:43:46,165 --> 00:43:47,871
這是銀行嗎？
Is this the bank?

707
00:43:47,959 --> 00:43:49,745
是的。我上去嗎？
Yes. Shall I come up?

708
00:43:49,836 --> 00:43:52,578
不用了，你可以在樓下等。
No, but you're welcome down here.

709
00:43:55,800 --> 00:43:57,006
明白了。
Got it.

710
00:44:11,983 --> 00:44:14,269
希望我在村子裏穿得不過分隆重。
I hope I'm not overdressed for the village.

711
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:15,725
不會的，我不會這麼說。
No, I wouldn't say so.

712
00:44:15,820 --> 00:44:17,685
進來，認識大家吧。
Come on in and meet everybody.

713
00:44:18,322 --> 00:44:20,563
大家，這是 James Elcott。
Everybody, meet James Elcott.

714
00:44:33,212 --> 00:44:35,578
你這打扮不像個銀行家。
You're dressed funny for a banker.

715
00:44:35,673 --> 00:44:38,460
- 我可以回家換衣服。 - 哦，不，我覺得很可愛。
- I could go home and change. - Oh, no, I think it's sweet.

716
00:44:38,551 --> 00:44:40,792
你爲我們打扮，我們也爲你打扮。
You dressed for us and we dressed for you.

717
00:44:41,846 --> 00:44:43,427
Penelope，幫忙。
Penelope, help.

718
00:44:43,514 --> 00:44:44,992
你知道這種場合會讓我緊張。
You know these things make me nervous.

719
00:44:45,016 --> 00:44:46,927
別慌，Sebastian。救援馬上到。
Don't panic, Sebastian. Help is on the way.

720
00:44:47,018 --> 00:44:49,885
- 我就一會兒。 - 我會記着你的。
- I'll just be a sec. - I'm going to hold you to that.

721
00:44:49,979 --> 00:44:51,719
我瞭解你。
I know you.

722
00:44:51,814 --> 00:44:53,930
你在市聯邦銀行存錢嗎？
Do you bank at city federal?

723
00:44:54,025 --> 00:44:55,390
我把錢塞在牀墊裏。
I bank in my mattress.

724
00:44:55,484 --> 00:44:57,440
那也不錯。
Well, that's nice too.

725
00:44:57,528 --> 00:44:59,940
昨晚在 Plush Pig，
Last night at plush pig,

726
00:45:00,031 --> 00:45:01,521
你在我重要的那段演出時走了。
you walked out on my big number.

727
00:45:01,616 --> 00:45:03,106
是個無心的冒犯。
An unintentional slight.

728
00:45:03,201 --> 00:45:05,943
話說得輕巧。現在想聽嗎？
Talk's cheap. Wanna hear it now?

729
00:45:06,037 --> 00:45:08,824
- 就在這兒，沒有你的樂隊？ - 我會假唱給你聽。
- Right here without your band? - I'll fake it for you.

730
00:45:08,915 --> 00:45:10,701
我要去把我的朋友從 Boom Boom 那兒救出來。
I've got to rescue my friend from boom boom.

731
00:45:10,791 --> 00:45:12,281
我要去救那位商人。
I shall rescue the businessman.

732
00:45:12,376 --> 00:45:13,912
請把我的禮物講完。
Please finish my present.

733
00:45:14,545 --> 00:45:17,127
畢竟這是你的生日。
Well, it's your birthday.

734
00:45:17,215 --> 00:45:18,775
來段《Greensleeves》快版如何？
How about a fast arrangement of "Greensleeves?"

735
00:45:18,799 --> 00:45:20,209
等一下，Boom Boom。那個人是我的。
Just a minute, boom boom. He's mine.

736
00:45:20,301 --> 00:45:22,212
哦，拜託，Sebastian。
Oh, come on, Sebastian.

737
00:45:29,435 --> 00:45:31,300
我敢說你在哪兒都能適應。
I bet you fit in any place.

738
00:45:31,938 --> 00:45:35,055
- 我喜歡你的朋友。 - 他們隨租約一塊來的。
- I like your friends. - They came with the lease.

739
00:45:35,149 --> 00:45:36,980
那也隨租約帶來的嗎？
Did that come with the lease too?

740
00:45:37,068 --> 00:45:40,185
不是。我曾和一個焊工約會過。
No. I used to date this welder.

741
00:45:40,279 --> 00:45:42,486
他一定是個糟糕的司機。
He must have been an awful driver.

742
00:45:42,573 --> 00:45:46,282
不，我還有一個男朋友，開廢品場的。
No, I had this other boyfriend who owns a junkyard.

743
00:45:46,369 --> 00:45:48,030
你男朋友真多，不是嗎？
You got a lot of boyfriends, haven't you?

744
00:45:48,120 --> 00:45:50,281
嗯。你是我的第一個銀行家。
Hm. You're my first banker.

745
00:45:50,373 --> 00:45:51,613
爲什麼要到處逛？
Why all this shopping around?

746
00:45:51,707 --> 00:45:53,447
如果你不試所有東西，
Well, if you don't try everything

747
00:45:53,542 --> 00:45:55,828
怎麼知道自己真正喜歡什麼？
how are you gonna find out what you really like?

748
00:45:57,046 --> 00:45:59,128
孩童之言真是金玉良言。
Out of the mouths of babes.

749
00:46:14,397 --> 00:46:15,682
又來？
Again?

750
00:46:29,412 --> 00:46:31,277
大家都去哪兒了？
Where did everybody go?

751
00:46:32,248 --> 00:46:33,658
他們都在這兒。
They're all here.

752
00:46:47,888 --> 00:46:49,924
三週後，我們結婚了。
Three weeks later, we got married.

753
00:46:50,016 --> 00:46:53,474
匆匆忙忙，好像不結婚會死掉似的。
All in a rush. Like if we didn't, we'd die.

754
00:46:53,561 --> 00:46:55,643
如果你老公還是那個
And if your husband was still the same

755
00:46:55,730 --> 00:46:57,846
浪漫格林威治村 James，
romantic Greenwich village James,

756
00:46:57,940 --> 00:46:59,805
你現在還會去偷東西嗎？
would you be stealing now?

757
00:46:59,900 --> 00:47:02,391
哦，James 沒有時間談浪漫了。
Oh, James hasn't got time for romance.

758
00:47:02,486 --> 00:47:04,522
他太忙於銀行工作。
He's too busy banking.

759
00:47:04,613 --> 00:47:05,898
所以你還偷嗎？
So you steal?

760
00:47:06,907 --> 00:47:09,114
你對這事過於冷靜了。
You're much too calm about it.

761
00:47:09,201 --> 00:47:10,816
我爲什麼不能冷靜？
Well, why shouldn't I be calm?

762
00:47:10,911 --> 00:47:13,402
畢竟，沒有什麼能把我和搶劫聯繫起來。
After all, there's nothing to connect me with the robbery.

763
00:47:14,915 --> 00:47:16,906
除了那件黃色套裝。
Except the yellow suit.

764
00:47:17,001 --> 00:47:19,413
你知道警察在全城搜尋它嗎。
You realize the police are combing the city for it.

765
00:47:19,503 --> 00:47:21,664
嗯，我有看到報道。
Mm, so I've read.

766
00:47:21,756 --> 00:47:23,462
我已經處理掉了。
I took care of it.

767
00:47:23,549 --> 00:47:24,584
你把它燒了嗎？
You burned it?

768
00:47:24,675 --> 00:47:27,041
沒有，我把它捐給了舊貨店。
No, I gave it away to a thrift shop.

769
00:47:27,136 --> 00:47:28,421
舊貨店？
Thrift shop?

770
00:47:28,512 --> 00:47:30,032
你知道你這樣做有多冒險嗎？
Do you realize the chance you're taking?

771
00:47:30,056 --> 00:47:31,842
我不知道。
I don't know.

772
00:47:31,932 --> 00:47:33,672
也許我會去把它買回來。
Maybe I'll go buy it back.

773
00:47:33,768 --> 00:47:35,850
買回來？不，不行！
Buy it? No, no!

774
00:47:35,936 --> 00:47:37,142
Penny，看。
Penny, look.

775
00:47:37,229 --> 00:47:39,185
你這是想被抓嗎，嗯？
Are you trying to get caught, mm?

776
00:47:39,273 --> 00:47:41,168
你根本就不該去那兒。
You never should have gone there in the first place.

777
00:47:41,192 --> 00:47:43,478
那我還能怎麼辦？把它扔掉？
Well, what else could I do? Throw it away?

778
00:47:43,569 --> 00:47:45,230
那樣會安全得多。
It would have been a lot safer.

779
00:47:45,321 --> 00:47:48,358
Gregory，那是件 Givenchy 套裝。
Gregory, it was a Givenchy suit.

780
00:47:48,449 --> 00:47:49,780
然後呢？
So?

781
00:47:49,867 --> 00:47:52,324
你不能把 Givenchy 扔進下水道。
Well, you can't just throw a Givenchy down a manhole.

782
00:47:52,411 --> 00:47:53,696
那簡直是褻瀆。
It's sacrilege.

783
00:47:53,788 --> 00:47:56,700
再說，James 爲那套衣服付了1100美元，
And besides, James paid $1100 for that suit

784
00:47:56,791 --> 00:47:59,453
我可不想看到他浪費錢。
and I wouldn't like to see him waste his money.

785
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:23,143
嗨。Bixbee 中尉。羅斯柴爾德中士。
Hi. Lieutenant Bixbee. Sergeant Rothschild.

786
00:48:23,234 --> 00:48:24,644
真是個意外的驚喜。
What a nice surprise.

787
00:48:24,735 --> 00:48:27,568
Elcott 太太，你經常來這兒買嗎？
Mrs. Elcott, do you shop here?

788
00:48:27,655 --> 00:48:30,897
是的，我常來。他們有許多有趣的東西。
Yes, I often drop by. They have fascinating things.

789
00:48:30,991 --> 00:48:33,824
他們昨天確實有。那兒有那件黃色套裝。
They did yesterday. They had the yellow suit.

790
00:48:33,911 --> 00:48:35,902
並非完全如此。
Not really.

791
00:48:35,996 --> 00:48:36,996
他們怎麼得到的？
How did they get it?

792
00:48:37,081 --> 00:48:38,183
嗯，他們得到它的方式和
Well, they got it the same way

793
00:48:38,207 --> 00:48:40,619
Higgins 少校弄到那張1000美元鈔票的方式一樣。
that major Higgins got his $1000 bill.

794
00:48:40,709 --> 00:48:43,701
是個金髮的女孩捐的，她帶着裝出來的法國口音。
It was donated by a blond girl with a phony French accent.

795
00:48:43,796 --> 00:48:46,003
- 然後我們追查到了這裏。 - 真聰明啊你們。
- And we traced it here. - Well, how clever of you.

796
00:48:46,090 --> 00:48:47,317
也沒那麼聰明。
Well, not so clever.

797
00:48:47,341 --> 00:48:50,003
後面那位女士在報上看到後打電話給我們。
The lady back there read about it in the paper and called us.

798
00:48:50,094 --> 00:48:52,005
但我們還夠聰明，接了電話。
But we were clever enough to pick up the phone.

799
00:48:54,348 --> 00:48:56,339
好，那就這樣。你們找到了。
Well, that's that. You've got it.

800
00:48:56,434 --> 00:48:58,925
還沒呢。有人買走了。只付了七塊錢。
Not yet. Somebody bought it. Paid seven bucks.

801
00:48:59,019 --> 00:49:02,136
- 七塊？那…… - 怎麼了？太便宜嗎？
- Seven bucks? But that... - What? Too cheap?

802
00:49:02,231 --> 00:49:04,267
這也說不準。
Well, that's hard to say.

803
00:49:04,358 --> 00:49:05,723
我得先看看。
I'd have to see it first.

804
00:49:05,818 --> 00:49:07,712
那你爲何不和我們一塊去拿呢？
Well, why don't you come along while we pick it up?

805
00:49:07,736 --> 00:49:09,146
我能坐警車嗎？
Do I get to ride in a police car?

806
00:49:09,238 --> 00:49:11,900
可以，有警笛，還有一切配備。
Yeah, with a siren and everything.

807
00:49:19,123 --> 00:49:21,705
羅斯柴爾德中士總是這麼開車嗎？
Does sergeant Rothschild always drive like that?

808
00:49:21,792 --> 00:49:23,999
他只是稍微賣弄一下而已。
He was just showin' off a little.

809
00:49:25,421 --> 00:49:27,912
這是我第一次有機會參加警察突襲。
This is the first police raid I've ever been invited to.

810
00:49:28,007 --> 00:49:29,713
你們要把門撞開嗎？
Are you gonna break down the door?

811
00:49:29,800 --> 00:49:32,257
那種做法隨禁酒令時代一起過去了。
Well, you see, that went out with prohibition.

812
00:49:32,344 --> 00:49:34,255
現在我們有了全新的形象。
Now we have a whole new image.

813
00:49:34,346 --> 00:49:36,678
既時髦又有禮貌。
It's very suave and very couth.

814
00:49:37,099 --> 00:49:40,557
所以進去後，你就跟着我做就行了。
So when we get inside, you just take your cue from me.

815
00:49:40,644 --> 00:49:41,644
明白，長官。
Right, chief.

816
00:49:41,729 --> 00:49:43,390
那是中尉，Elcott 太太。
That's lieutenant, Mrs. Elcott.

817
00:49:43,481 --> 00:49:44,937
那是 Penelope，中尉。
That's Penelope, lieutenant.

818
00:49:45,024 --> 00:49:48,733
Horatio。我的父親很愛讀書。
Horatio. My father read a lot.

819
00:49:55,826 --> 00:49:57,316
嗯。嗯。
Mm. Mm.

820
00:49:58,454 --> 00:50:00,695
嗯。嗯。
Mm. Mm.

821
00:50:04,168 --> 00:50:06,124
哦，親愛的。
Oh, cherie.

822
00:50:06,212 --> 00:50:09,579
這纔是我認爲的經典醃牛肉三明治。
Now that's what I call a vintage pastrami.

823
00:50:09,673 --> 00:50:11,413
嗯哼。嗯。
Mm-hm. Mm.

824
00:50:11,509 --> 00:50:12,509
嗯。
Mm.

825
00:50:12,593 --> 00:50:14,709
美味的蒔蘿醃黃瓜...
Delish dill pickle...

826
00:50:15,846 --> 00:50:18,679
沒什麼好挑剔的。
Is nothing to throw rocks at.

827
00:50:22,978 --> 00:50:26,721
我感覺有點胃灼熱要起來了。
I feel a slight heartburn building up.

828
00:50:26,815 --> 00:50:28,851
快，我的天使，奶油汽水。
Quickly, my angel, the cream soda.

829
00:50:44,500 --> 00:50:48,413
啊，午安，女士們先生們。
Ah, good afternoon, lady and gentleman.

830
00:50:48,504 --> 00:50:50,836
歡迎來到Princess Sadaba的沙龍。
Welcome to the salon of Princess Sadaba.

831
00:50:50,923 --> 00:50:53,289
這家精品店非常時髦。
The boutique très chic.

832
00:50:54,718 --> 00:50:58,677
- 你好。 - 啊，這國產香檳。
- Salut. - Ah, this domestic champagne.

833
00:50:58,764 --> 00:51:02,803
啊，Princess Sadaba能爲您做些什麼？
Ah, and what can Princess Sadaba do for you?

834
00:51:02,893 --> 00:51:05,680
別告訴我，我知道。
Don't tell me, I know.

835
00:51:05,771 --> 00:51:08,979
身材如此迷人，您顯然
With such a lovely figure, you have obviously

836
00:51:09,066 --> 00:51:12,809
是來爲Sadaba的某件華麗晚禮服而來。
come for one of Sadaba's divine evening gowns.

