我不知道。就是些人。
I don't know. Just people.

1005
00:59:55,675 --> 00:59:58,007
是的，人。
Yes, people. People who are your husband's

1006
00:59:58,095 --> 00:59:59,426
就是你丈夫的生意夥伴，對吧？
business associates, huh?

1007
00:59:59,513 --> 01:00:00,719
是的。
Yes.

1008
01:00:00,806 --> 01:00:04,594
不知爲什麼，我就是討厭他們。
For some reason, I just hated them.

1009
01:00:04,684 --> 01:00:05,964
無論我和 James 去哪兒，
No matter where James and I went

1010
01:00:06,019 --> 01:00:08,135
都甩不開金融界的那些事。
there was no getting away from the world of finance.

1011
01:00:08,230 --> 01:00:09,874
“總統關於稅收的聲明
"The president's statement on taxes

1012
01:00:09,898 --> 01:00:11,854
給市場帶來了拋售壓力。”
brought selling pressure into the market.

1013
01:00:11,942 --> 01:00:13,382
儘管他確實重申了那點……
And though he did reiterate that...

1014
01:00:13,443 --> 01:00:15,479
哦，我們去遊個泳吧。
Oh, let's go for a little swim.

1015
01:00:15,570 --> 01:00:17,811
呃，好吧……你不覺得現在有點晚了嗎？
Eh, well... don't you think it's late, isn't it?

1016
01:00:17,906 --> 01:00:19,442
哦，拜託。
Oh, come on.

1017
01:00:19,533 --> 01:00:21,819
在紐波特，是 Johanna Keller，
At Newport, it was Johanna Keller,

1018
01:00:21,910 --> 01:00:23,491
她是銀行最大的儲戶之一。
one of the bank's biggest depositors.

1019
01:00:23,578 --> 01:00:25,239
- 我最後吃的那根熱狗…… - 哦，拜託。
- The last hot dog I ate... - Oh, come on.

1020
01:00:25,330 --> 01:00:26,911
哦，求你了，小姐……
Oh, please, miss...

1021
01:00:51,940 --> 01:00:54,807
從那以後，我們就不怎麼見到 Keller 小姐了。
After that, we didn't see so much of miss Keller.

1022
01:00:54,898 --> 01:00:58,735
即便我們去跳舞，比如街區那晚，
Even when we'd go dancing, like the night at the block,

1023
01:00:58,822 --> 01:01:00,528
遲早，James 的銀行界朋友們
sooner or later, James' banking friends

1024
01:01:00,615 --> 01:01:02,822
會破壞我們的樂趣。
would manage to spoil our fun.

1025
01:01:02,909 --> 01:01:06,868
哦，遲早我得和他們談生意了。
Oh, sooner or later, I'm going to have to talk business with them.

1026
01:01:06,955 --> 01:01:08,161
我不明白爲什麼。
I don't see why.

1027
01:01:08,248 --> 01:01:10,705
畢竟，你又不是在銀行裏和他們跳舞，對吧？
After all, you don't dance with them at the bank, do you?

1028
01:01:10,792 --> 01:01:13,579
親愛的，我愛你。
I love you, darling.

1029
01:01:13,670 --> 01:01:16,252
我很慶幸不必和你談生意。
I'm glad I don't have to do business with you.

1030
01:01:16,339 --> 01:01:18,876
真不公平，你們倆。
Not fair, you two.

1031
01:01:18,967 --> 01:01:20,878
哦，那是“la Bostella”。
Oh, it's "la Bostella."

1032
01:01:20,969 --> 01:01:22,880
你就不能死嗎？
Couldn't you just die?

1033
01:01:22,971 --> 01:01:25,553
音樂一停，我們就都倒下。
When the music stops, we all fall down.

1034
01:01:43,992 --> 01:01:45,983
我就得收拾他一下。
I just had to fix him.

1035
01:01:50,874 --> 01:01:52,614
不錯。
Not bad.

1036
01:01:53,084 --> 01:01:55,416
鑽石王冠，三枚胸針，
Diamond tiara, three brooches,

1037
01:01:55,503 --> 01:01:58,836
九條手鐲和一條掛式項鍊。
nine bracelets and a lavaliere.

1038
01:01:58,924 --> 01:02:01,006
哦，我最精彩的一次是我拿走了……
Oh, and my best caper was when I took...

1039
01:02:01,134 --> 01:02:03,216
Penny，別說了。別說了。
Penny, just stop. Just stop.

1040
01:02:03,303 --> 01:02:05,794
但那還遠遠不止這些。
我可以講好幾個小時。
But there's lots more. I could go on for hours.

1041
01:02:05,889 --> 01:02:08,175
也許你可以，但我可做不到。
Maybe you could, but I couldn't.

1042
01:02:08,266 --> 01:02:11,099
Gregory，你千萬別因此沮喪。
Gregory, you mustn't let this depress you.

1043
01:02:12,062 --> 01:02:13,643
沮喪是一種奢侈，
Depression is a luxury

1044
01:02:13,730 --> 01:02:16,187
經驗豐富的精神科醫生是不能沉溺其中的。
not permitted the experienced psychiatrist.

1045
01:02:16,274 --> 01:02:17,559
嗯，那很好。
Well, that's good.

1046
01:02:17,651 --> 01:02:19,651
因爲這件事也有積極的一面。
Because there is a bright side to this whole thing.

1047
01:02:22,113 --> 01:02:24,274
按我那時婚姻的走向來看，
Well, the way my marriage was headed

1048
01:02:24,366 --> 01:02:25,856
以及我那時的神經狀態，
and the state of nerves I was in,

1049
01:02:25,951 --> 01:02:27,657
要不是有竊盜癖在，我
if it hadn't been for kleptomania

1050
01:02:27,744 --> 01:02:29,655
可能真會有點兒精神失常。
I might have gone a little kook.

1051
01:02:32,666 --> 01:02:34,873
Penny，你知道當你的分析師有多難嗎？
Penny, do you have any idea how difficult

1052
01:02:34,960 --> 01:02:36,496
你知道嗎，做你的分析師可不容易。
it is being your analyst?

1053
01:02:36,586 --> 01:02:38,372
哦，Gregory，你應該在認識我之前就見過我，
Oh, Gregory, you should have known me

1054
01:02:38,463 --> 01:02:39,999
那時候的我
in the days before you knew me.

1055
01:02:40,090 --> 01:02:42,331
很模糊、很輕浮。
I was vague, frivolous.

1056
01:02:42,425 --> 01:02:44,381
你甚至可以說我有點兒神經質。
You might even say a bit of a ding.

1057
01:02:44,469 --> 01:02:46,960
謝天謝地，我已經安定下來了。再見。
Thank heaven, I've settled down. Bye.

1058
01:02:55,188 --> 01:02:56,598
你認爲忘鞋子意味着什麼呢？
What do you suppose it means

1059
01:02:56,690 --> 01:02:59,898
當你老是忘記鞋子時，這意味着什麼？嗯。
when you keep forgetting your shoes? Hm.

1060
01:02:59,985 --> 01:03:01,963
你要急到哪裏去？你還有七分鐘。
Where are you rushing to? You still have seven minutes left.

1061
01:03:01,987 --> 01:03:04,444
哦，你可以記在賬上。我得去 Park Lane 畫廊了。
Oh, you can owe me. I'm off to the park Lane galleries.

1062
01:03:04,531 --> 01:03:06,613
那裏有一幅倫勃朗，簡直是撿便宜。
There's a Rembrandt there that's a steal.

1063
01:03:10,120 --> 01:03:13,032
倫勃朗。Penny，你不會真的去偷吧。
A Rembrandt. Penny, you wouldn't.

1064
01:03:15,166 --> 01:03:17,157
出租車！出租車！
Taxi! Taxi!

1065
01:03:50,577 --> 01:03:52,192
噓。
Psst.

1066
01:03:52,287 --> 01:03:53,948
噓。
Psst.

1067
01:03:54,039 --> 01:03:55,039
Gregory。噓！
Gregory. Shh!

1068
01:03:55,123 --> 01:03:56,408
什麼？警察來了。
What? Police.

1069
01:03:58,084 --> 01:04:00,700
他們可能跟蹤我來了。警察？
They may have followed me. Police?

1070
01:04:00,795 --> 01:04:03,832
Gregory，你到底做了什麼？
Gregory, what have you done?

1071
01:04:03,923 --> 01:04:05,788
什麼都沒做。我什麼都沒做。
Nothing. I haven't done anything.

1072
01:04:06,885 --> 01:04:07,987
好吧，如果你什麼都沒做，
Well, if you haven't done anything

1073
01:04:08,011 --> 01:04:09,071
那警察爲什麼會——
then why would the police...

1074
01:04:09,095 --> 01:04:13,259
Penelope，我現在不想爭論。現在告訴我，你把錢藏在哪兒了？
Penelope, I don't want to get into a discussion, not now.

1075
01:04:13,350 --> 01:04:16,683
現在告訴我，你把錢藏在哪兒了？
Now tell me, where, where did you hide the money?

1076
01:04:16,770 --> 01:04:17,770
什麼錢？
What money?

1077
01:04:17,854 --> 01:04:19,765
你說“什麼錢”是什麼意思？你知道的……
What do you mean, what money? You know what...

1078
01:04:20,815 --> 01:04:23,022
贓款。那筆贓款。
Loot. The loot.

1079
01:04:23,109 --> 01:04:24,940
哦，那個錢。
Oh, that money.

1080
01:04:25,028 --> 01:04:28,737
說實話，那事讓我很擔心。
Well, frankly, that's had me very worried.

1081
01:04:28,823 --> 01:04:31,360
我的意思是，我不能就把它隨便放在某個地方。
I mean, I couldn't just leave it lying around any place.

1082
01:04:31,451 --> 01:04:34,284
你知道的，那樣很不安全。
You know, that could be very dodgy.

1083
01:04:34,371 --> 01:04:36,282
我一直隨身帶着……哦！
I carry it with... oh!

1084
01:04:46,841 --> 01:04:48,377
你們的中尉 Bixbee 知道了。
Your lieutenant Bixbee, he knows.

1085
01:04:48,468 --> 01:04:49,583
他剛來見過我。
He just came to see me.

1086
01:04:49,677 --> 01:04:52,293
我覺得他昨天舉止有些奇怪。
I thought he acted strangely yesterday.

1087
01:04:52,389 --> 01:04:53,925
奇怪？怎麼奇怪？
Strangely how?

1088
01:04:54,015 --> 01:04:57,678
我也說不上來。有點……內疚的樣子。
I don't know. Sort of... guilty.

1089
01:04:57,769 --> 01:05:00,135
他爲什麼會覺得內疚？哦，算了。噢！
Why would he feel guilty? Oh, never mind. Ooh!

1090
01:05:04,859 --> 01:05:05,859
Penny，聽我說。
Penny, listen to me.

1091
01:05:05,944 --> 01:05:07,671
你必須今天就把那筆錢送回銀行。
You've got to get that money back to the bank today.

1092
01:05:07,695 --> 01:05:09,560
現在。怎麼做？
Now. How?

1093
01:05:09,656 --> 01:05:11,271
我不能就走進去把錢交上去。
I can't just walk in and hand it over.

1094
01:05:11,366 --> 01:05:12,776
嗯，我想過……
Well, I figured that...

1095
01:05:12,867 --> 01:05:13,982
哦，把錢給我吧，
Oh, give me the money

1096
01:05:14,077 --> 01:05:16,284
我會把它放進夜間存款口。
and I'll, I'll stick it in the night deposit chute.

1097
01:05:16,371 --> 01:05:19,113
哦，Gregory，我不想你牽扯進來。
Oh, Gregory, I don't like to see you get involved.

1098
01:05:19,207 --> 01:05:20,868
我也不想。
Neither do I.

1099
01:05:20,959 --> 01:05:22,870
來吧，把所有的都給我。
Come on. All of it.

1100
01:05:26,840 --> 01:05:28,171
哦，Penny。
Oh, penny.

1101
01:05:42,480 --> 01:05:43,765
Penny.
Penny.

1102
01:05:43,857 --> 01:05:45,472
- 好了，我看起來如何？
- 看起來很害怕。
- Alright, how do I look? - Frightened.

1103
01:05:45,567 --> 01:05:47,808
哦，不，我是說頭部這兒。
Oh, no, I mean up here.

1104
01:05:47,902 --> 01:05:49,733
- 像蝙蝠俠。 - 謝謝。
- Like Batman. - Thanks.

1105
01:05:49,821 --> 01:05:51,812
Gregory，你真體貼。
Gregory, you're very sweet.

1106
01:05:51,906 --> 01:05:53,942
但你爲什麼非要這麼做不可？
But why do you insist on doing this?

1107
01:05:54,033 --> 01:05:55,819
因爲我愛你。
Because I'm in love with you.

1108
01:05:55,910 --> 01:05:57,696
因爲我對你癡狂。 - Gregory.
- Because I'm crazy about you. - Gregory.

1109
01:05:57,787 --> 01:06:00,529
當我說癡狂時，我是醫學上說的那種。
And when I say crazy, I'm using the word medically.

1110
01:06:00,623 --> 01:06:02,143
- 但就在前幾天…… - 算了。
- But just the other day... - Forget it.

1111
01:06:02,167 --> 01:06:04,624
- 你說了…… - 算了，算了！
- You said... - Forget it. Forget it!

1112
01:06:04,711 --> 01:06:09,421
現在我們走吧，儘量表現得很自然。
Now let's get out of here and try to act very natural.

1113
01:06:24,939 --> 01:06:27,601
- 他們把我們鎖起來了！ - 別擔心。
- They locked us in! - Don't worry.

1114
01:06:27,692 --> 01:06:28,919
那鈴鐺應該會有人來。
That bell ought to bring somebody.

1115
01:06:28,943 --> 01:06:31,855
那鈴鐺會把所有人都引來。那是盜賊警報。
That bell will bring everybody. That's a burglar alarm.

1116
01:06:31,946 --> 01:06:33,857
- 要是他們搜我們怎麼辦？ - 那又怎樣？
- What if they search us? - Well, what of it?

1117
01:06:33,948 --> 01:06:36,010
- 我們沒有偷東西。 - 今天沒偷東西。
- We haven't stolen anything. - Not today, we haven't.

1118
01:06:36,034 --> 01:06:37,194
你以爲這是什麼地方？
What do you think this is?

1119
01:06:37,285 --> 01:06:39,742
- 哦，Penny。 - 他們不敢搜我們。
- Oh, penny. - They wouldn't dare search us.

1120
01:06:39,829 --> 01:06:42,741
喂喂，有人在嗎？喂！
Yoo-hoo, somebody! Yoo-hoo!

1121
01:06:42,832 --> 01:06:44,322
還不行！還不行！
Not yet! Not yet!

1122
01:06:44,417 --> 01:06:46,282
喂！喂！
Yoo-hoo! Yoo-hoo!

1123
01:06:48,671 --> 01:06:51,083
晚上好。你介意開門嗎？
Good evening. Would you mind opening the gate, please?

1124
01:06:51,174 --> 01:06:53,335
你們在裏面，幹什麼呢？
You in there, what are you up to?

1125
01:06:53,426 --> 01:06:54,962
什麼也沒幹。我發誓。
Nothing. I swear it.

1126
01:06:55,053 --> 01:06:56,964
請叫經理來。
Please call the manager.

1127
01:06:57,972 --> 01:07:00,384
我就是經理。
I am the manager.

1128
01:07:00,475 --> 01:07:02,841
關門時你們藏在哪裏了？
Where were you hiding when we locked up?

1129
01:07:02,936 --> 01:07:04,722
哦，就在那個櫥櫃後面。
Oh, right behind that cabinet.

1130
01:07:04,812 --> 01:07:05,956
不，我們沒有。我們沒藏。
No, we weren't. We weren't hiding.

1131
01:07:05,980 --> 01:07:07,345
我們站着，我們站着。
We were standing. We were standing.

1132
01:07:07,440 --> 01:07:09,726
你們不知道我們已經關門了嗎？
Don't you realize we're closed?

1133
01:07:09,817 --> 01:07:11,227
那正是問題所在。
Well, that's just the trouble.

1134
01:07:11,319 --> 01:07:13,901
如果你們開門，我們就能離開。
If you were open, we could leave.

1135
01:07:13,988 --> 01:07:16,149
別你們敢搜我們的身
And don't you dare try to search us

1136
01:07:16,241 --> 01:07:17,526
否則我們就報警。
or we'll call the police.

1137
01:07:17,617 --> 01:07:19,824
Penelope！她不是那個意思。
Penelope! She didn't mean that.

1138
01:07:19,911 --> 01:07:21,822
你不是那個意思。
You didn't mean that.

1139
01:07:23,540 --> 01:07:26,282
你算什麼，女士？有毛病嗎？
What are you, lady? Some kind of a nut?

1140
01:07:26,376 --> 01:07:28,492
我不喜歡你的態度。
I don't care for your attitude.

1141
01:07:28,586 --> 01:07:29,980
順便說一句，你見到
And for your information, you have seen

1142
01:07:30,004 --> 01:07:32,416
我這種人，這就是最後一次了。
the last of me in this gallery.

1143
01:07:32,507 --> 01:07:33,997
走吧，Gregory。
Come, Gregory.

1144
01:08:40,617 --> 01:08:43,074
早安，親愛的。喂。是的。
Morning, darling. Hello. Yeah.

1145
01:08:43,161 --> 01:08:44,367
嗯。
Yeah.

1146
01:08:45,413 --> 01:08:46,903
是的。
Yes.

1147
01:08:46,998 --> 01:08:49,489
什麼？你確定嗎？
What? You sure?

1148
01:08:49,584 --> 01:08:51,540
是的，我——真難相信。
Yeah, I-I find that hard to believe.

1149
01:08:53,796 --> 01:08:55,502
半小時後。
In, uh, half an hour.

1150
01:08:55,590 --> 01:08:56,625
好。
Right.

1151
01:08:57,967 --> 01:08:59,628
剛纔電話是誰的？
Who was that on the phone?

1152
01:08:59,719 --> 01:09:01,300
是銀行打來的。
The bank.

1153
01:09:01,387 --> 01:09:04,254
哦，他們想要什麼？
Oh, what'd they want?

1154
01:09:04,349 --> 01:09:06,089
誰想要什麼？
What did who want?

1155
01:09:06,184 --> 01:09:07,515
銀行。
The bank.

1156
01:09:07,602 --> 01:09:09,342
他們想和我談。
They wanted to talk to me.

1157
01:09:09,437 --> 01:09:11,553
- 關於什麼 - 關於銀行業的事。
- Well, what about? - About banking.

1158
01:09:12,982 --> 01:09:13,982
哦。
Oh.

1159
01:09:20,907 --> 01:09:23,865
好吧，他們把金融版放哪兒了？
Well, where did they hide the financial section?

1160
01:09:23,951 --> 01:09:26,693
你什麼時候開始關心錢的事了？
Since when have you been concerned with money matters?

1161
01:09:26,788 --> 01:09:29,029
我只是表示一點做妻子的關心。
I'm just showing a little wifely interest.

1162
01:09:34,796 --> 01:09:37,913
嗯，那真好笑。金融版嗎？
Well, that's funny. The financial section?

1163
01:09:39,092 --> 01:09:40,798
不，我只是希望……
No, I was just hoping...

1164
01:09:40,885 --> 01:09:42,216
- 早上好，Toshi。 - 早
- Morning, Toshi. - Morning.

1165
01:09:42,303 --> 01:09:43,759
我只是想也許會有
I just thought maybe there might be

1166
01:09:43,846 --> 01:09:45,115
關於那起搶劫案的一些好消息。
some good news about the robbery.

1167
01:09:45,139 --> 01:09:47,004
壞消息怎麼會有好消息？
How can there be good news about bad news?

1168
01:09:47,100 --> 01:09:50,558
嗯，有可能。你可能能把錢要回來。
Well, it's possible. You could get the money back.

1169
01:09:50,645 --> 01:09:52,306
那不會在財經版出現。
That wouldn't be in the financial section.

1170
01:09:52,397 --> 01:09:54,888
會登在宗教版的“奇蹟”欄目。
It would be on the religious page under miracles.

1171
01:09:54,982 --> 01:09:57,564
不過，你已經拿回那1000美元了。
Well, you already got that $1000 back.

1172
01:09:57,652 --> 01:09:59,296
希望我別用同樣的方式把其餘的錢也拿回來。
Let's hope I don't get the rest back the same way.

1173
01:09:59,320 --> 01:10:01,436
我可能會破產。
I could go broke.

1174
01:10:01,531 --> 01:10:04,568
James，你還是不明白那件事，不是嗎...
James, you still don't understand about that, do you...

1175
01:10:04,659 --> 01:10:05,899
現在我明白了，我明白了，我明白了。
Now I do, I do, I do.

1176
01:10:05,993 --> 01:10:07,304
好了，拜託，別再解釋了。
Now, please, don't explain it again.

1177
01:10:07,328 --> 01:10:09,865
我收支相抵了，我很高興，我欣喜若狂，是吧？
I broke even, I'm delighted, I'm delirious, huh?

1178
01:10:12,834 --> 01:10:14,995
嗯，你確實是收支平衡了。嗯。
Well, you did break even. Mm.

1179
01:10:18,256 --> 01:10:20,372
Mannix 醫生說你只是固執罷了。
Dr. Mannix says you're just being stubborn.

1180
01:10:20,466 --> 01:10:23,048
哦，Mannix 醫生這麼說的？
Oh, Dr. Mannix says that, does he?

1181
01:10:23,136 --> 01:10:24,296
是的，他說了。
Yes, he does.

1182
01:10:24,387 --> 01:10:27,003
Mannix 醫生怎麼會知道這事？
How does Dr. Mannix know anything about it?

1183
01:10:27,098 --> 01:10:28,804
嗯，因爲我告訴了他。
Well, I told him.

1184
01:10:30,268 --> 01:10:32,350
我告訴他一切。
I tell him everything.

1185
01:10:32,437 --> 01:10:34,143
什麼？一切？
What do you mean, everything?

1186
01:10:35,273 --> 01:10:36,513
一切。
Everything.

1187
01:10:36,607 --> 01:10:38,268
關於我也告訴了嗎？
About me too?

1188
01:10:38,735 --> 01:10:40,020
當然。
Well, of course.

1189
01:10:40,111 --> 01:10:42,648
我想我會去和你的 Mannix 醫生談談。
I think I'll have a talk with your Dr. Mannix.

1190
01:10:42,739 --> 01:10:45,355
James，那太好了。
James, that's marvelous.

1191
01:10:45,450 --> 01:10:47,657
你無法想象他能幫到你多少。
You have no idea how much he could help you.

1192
01:10:47,744 --> 01:10:49,450
我不想要幫助。
I don't want help.

1193
01:10:49,537 --> 01:10:51,073
那爲何要浪費錢？
Well, then why waste the money?

1194
01:10:51,164 --> 01:10:53,075
Bixbee 中尉。
Lieutenant Bixbee.

1195
01:10:56,794 --> 01:10:58,955
你們的錢...
Your money...

1196
01:10:59,046 --> 01:11:00,161
我們都找回來了。
We got it all back.

1197
01:11:00,256 --> 01:11:01,256
我就知道。
I knew it.

1198
01:11:01,340 --> 01:11:03,046
看來我低估你了，Bixbee。
Seems I underestimated you, Bixbee.

1199
01:11:03,134 --> 01:11:05,112
我想請你去局裏一趟。
I thought maybe you'd like to go down to headquarters.

1200
01:11:05,136 --> 01:11:08,469
你看，我們也抓到了偷錢的那個女孩。
You see, we also got the girl who stole it.

1201
01:11:08,556 --> 01:11:10,547
我們現在要把她帶去審問。
We're bringing her up for questioning now.

1202
01:11:11,476 --> 01:11:12,682
Toshi，我的帽子！
Toshi, my hat!

1203
01:11:12,769 --> 01:11:14,259
我不明白。
I don't understand.

1204
01:11:14,353 --> 01:11:17,140
嗯，你知道嗎，這事也讓我有些意外。
Well, you know, it kind of took me by surprise too.

1205
01:11:17,231 --> 01:11:20,064
我以爲我把案子想透了。
I thought I had this case all figured out.

1206
01:11:20,151 --> 01:11:22,062
- 準備好。- 好了，中尉。
- Goes to show you. - Ready, lieutenant.

1207
01:11:22,320 --> 01:11:24,060
等一下，James，我要跟你一起去。
Wait a minute. James, I'll go with you.

1208
01:11:24,155 --> 01:11:26,508
不，不，親愛的，你沒必要捲進這件事。
No, no, darling, there's no need for you to be involved in this.

1209
01:11:26,532 --> 01:11:28,488
等我！等我！
Wait for me! Wait for me!

1210
01:11:33,206 --> 01:11:37,495
Horatio，如果你們逮錯人怎麼辦？
Horatio, what if you've arrested the wrong girl?

1211
01:11:37,585 --> 01:11:38,585
絕無可能。
Not a chance.

1212
01:11:38,669 --> 01:11:41,206
我們抓她的時候，她身上就有那筆錢。
She had the money on her when we picked her up.

1213
01:11:41,297 --> 01:11:43,583
好吧。往這邊來。
Alright. Right this way.

1214
01:11:48,971 --> 01:11:50,882
哦，嗨，寶貝。
Oh, hi, doll.

1215
01:11:50,973 --> 01:11:52,884
你是新來的嗎，不是嗎？
Well, you're new in here, aren't you?

1216
01:11:52,975 --> 01:11:54,787
我是說，我不記得在夜間法庭見過你。
I mean, I don't recall making your acquaintance

1217
01:11:54,811 --> 01:11:56,642
in night court or nothin'.

1218
01:11:58,981 --> 01:12:00,972
我叫 Honeysuckle Rose。
Mine's honeysuckle Rose.

1219
01:12:01,150 --> 01:12:02,890
看起來你過得不錯。
You must be doing pretty good.

1220
01:12:02,985 --> 01:12:04,850
那件看起來差點像是真的貂皮。
That almost looks like for-real mink.

1221
01:12:04,946 --> 01:12:07,653
好了，Rose小姐。別動，放鬆一下。
Alright, miss Rose. Just hold it. Relax a minute.

1222
01:12:07,740 --> 01:12:09,571
不是冒犯您，Elcott太太。
No offense, Mrs. Elcott.

1223
01:12:09,659 --> 01:12:12,947
那穿真貂皮的女士是這位先生的太太，
The lady in the genuine mink is the wife of this gentleman,

1224
01:12:13,037 --> 01:12:15,870
正好是你們被搶的那家銀行的行長。
who happens to be the president of the bank that you hit.

1225
01:12:17,208 --> 01:12:18,493
哦。
Oh.

1226
01:12:19,001 --> 01:12:20,787
她看起來確實有點像…
Well, she looks pretty enough to be...

1227
01:12:20,878 --> 01:12:22,243
你真名叫什麼，親愛的？
What's your right name, honey?

1228
01:12:22,338 --> 01:12:24,750
我不是跟你說了嗎，Honeysuckle Rose。
Well, I told you. Honeysuckle Rose.

1229
01:12:24,841 --> 01:12:26,832
我姐姐叫 Mexicali Rose。
My sister's Mexicali Rose.

1230
01:12:26,926 --> 01:12:29,793
我知道，都是 Washington Square 的那些“玫瑰”。
I know, the roses of Washington square.

1231
01:12:29,887 --> 01:12:31,468
Huntington，West Virginia。
Huntington, West Virginia.

1232
01:12:31,556 --> 01:12:33,763
我們曾經開車經過那裏，James，還記得嗎？
We drove through there once, James, remember?

1233
01:12:33,850 --> 01:12:35,702
Penelope，拜託。我們能繼續了嗎？
Penelope, please. Can't we get on with this, hm?

1234
01:12:35,726 --> 01:12:37,637
Honeysuckle，你能不能做個乖孩子
Honeysuckle, why don't you be a good girl

1235
01:12:37,728 --> 01:12:39,764
好好把話說清楚，坦白承認？
and just give us a full confession?

1236
01:12:41,357 --> 01:12:43,769
嗯，好吧。
Hm, okay.

1237
01:12:43,860 --> 01:12:47,944
呃，我昨晚在 Park Avenue 遛貓
Um, I was walking my cat up park Avenue

1238
01:12:48,030 --> 01:12:49,986
大約，呃，凌晨三點左右
around, uh, 3 o'clock this morning

1239
01:12:50,074 --> 01:12:54,818
我看到那東西幾乎就躺在人行道上。
when I see that lying on the sidewalk... practically.

1240
01:12:54,912 --> 01:12:56,868
更正一下。你是走進了我的銀行
Correction. You walked into my bank

1241
01:12:56,956 --> 01:12:58,141
大約下午3點左右
around 3 o'clock in the afternoon

1242
01:12:58,165 --> 01:13:00,076
兩天前，偷走了那筆錢。
two days ago and stole the money.

1243
01:13:00,167 --> 01:13:01,953
等會兒。
Now wait a minute.

1244
01:13:02,044 --> 01:13:04,956
我看起來像會搶銀行的人嗎？
Do I look like a person who'd stick up a bank?

1245
01:13:05,047 --> 01:13:06,207
當然不是。
Of course not.

1246
01:13:06,299 --> 01:13:09,587
哎呦，凌晨三點遛貓有什麼不對嗎？
Oh, come now, walking a cat at 3 o'clock in the morning?

1247
01:13:09,677 --> 01:13:11,633
我看不出有什麼不對。
I don't see anything wrong with that.

1248
01:13:11,721 --> 01:13:13,461
她可能做的是夜班工作。
She probably does night work.

1249
01:13:13,556 --> 01:13:15,842
- 你是嗎？ - 嗯，呃……
- Do you? - Well, uh...

1250
01:13:17,143 --> 01:13:18,178
是的。
Yeah.

1251
01:13:18,895 --> 01:13:20,055
看吧？
You see?

1252
01:13:20,146 --> 01:13:22,228
好吧，事情總算定下來了。
Well, I'm glad we got that decided.

1253
01:13:22,315 --> 01:13:25,807
Penelope，我覺得你並沒有看清全貌。
Penelope, I don't think you're getting the full picture.

1254
01:13:25,902 --> 01:13:29,065
你看，對 Rose 小姐的指控
You see, the charge against miss Rose here

1255
01:13:29,155 --> 01:13:32,272
不是遛貓，而是搶銀行。
is not cat-walking, it's bank-robbing.

1256
01:13:32,366 --> 01:13:34,072
這是陷害。
Well, it's a frame.

1257
01:13:34,160 --> 01:13:37,243
我發誓我從沒進過那家銀行。
I never set foot inside that bank, I swear it.

1258
01:13:37,330 --> 01:13:38,911
我相信你。
I believe you.

1259
01:13:39,373 --> 01:13:42,410
但他們不信。
Well, but they don't.

1260
01:13:42,501 --> 01:13:44,867
看看他們的表情！
Well, look at their faces!

1261
01:13:44,962 --> 01:13:47,294
哦，這可不是30天服刑就完事的案子。
Oh, this is no 30 days and out rap.

1262
01:13:47,381 --> 01:13:50,214
他們要把我關起來，扔掉鑰匙。
They-they wanna lock me up and throw away the key.

1263
01:13:50,301 --> 01:13:53,714
親愛的，相信我，你堅持這個荒謬的說法只會讓自己更難受
Honey, believe me, you're only making it tough on yourself

1264
01:13:53,804 --> 01:13:55,795
一直堅持這種荒唐的故事。
by sticking to this cockamamie story.

1265
01:13:55,890 --> 01:13:58,256
那是我唯一會編的荒誕故事！
Well, that's the only cockamamie story I know!

1266
01:13:58,351 --> 01:13:59,786
好了，女管理員，把她帶出去。
Alright, matron, get her out of here.

1267
01:13:59,810 --> 01:14:02,176
哦，不，等等。
Oh, no. No, wait.

1268
01:14:02,271 --> 01:14:04,478
等等，我…我承認。
Wait, I-I-l admit it.

1269
01:14:04,565 --> 01:14:06,726
我撒謊了。
Lied.

1270
01:14:06,817 --> 01:14:09,274
那錢並不是放在路邊的。
The-the money w-wasn't on the sidewalk.

1271
01:14:09,362 --> 01:14:12,229
是從存款口裏露出來的。
I-it was sticking out of the deposit slot.

1272
01:14:12,323 --> 01:14:16,066
本來我是要把它送回去的，或許還能拿點賞金。
Well, I was gonna return it. Maybe collect a reward even.

1273
01:14:16,160 --> 01:14:18,071
但那不會讓我成了搶銀行的壞人，對吧？
But that doesn't make me a bank robber, does it?

1274
01:14:18,162 --> 01:14:20,744
我是說，不是他們所說的那種意思。
I mean, not-not like they mean.

1275
01:14:20,831 --> 01:14:23,368
等等，等等。
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

1276
01:14:23,459 --> 01:14:25,324
你們犯了個可怕的錯誤。
You're making a terrible mistake.

1277
01:14:25,419 --> 01:14:27,080
親愛的，他們知道自己在做什麼。
Honey, they know what they're doing.

1278
01:14:27,171 --> 01:14:29,503
那你怎麼知道她沒有說實話？
Well, how do you know that she isn't telling the truth?

1279
01:14:29,590 --> 01:14:32,548
這是我的推測。事情完全可能按她說的那樣發生過。
It's my theory. It could have happened exactly as she said it.

1280
01:14:32,635 --> 01:14:35,672
你是說有人真的把59,000美元
You mean somebody actually left $59,000

1281
01:14:35,763 --> 01:14:38,470
在深夜放在銀行門口？
on the doorstep of a bank in the middle of the night?

1282
01:14:38,557 --> 01:14:40,718
- 是的！ - 誰，Elcott太太？
- Yes! - Who, Mrs. Elcott?

1283
01:14:41,852 --> 01:14:44,264
小偷，就是那人。搶銀行的那位。
The thief, that's who. The bank robber.

1284
01:14:44,355 --> 01:14:46,095
親愛的，出於什麼理由呢？
For what possible reason, darling?

1285
01:14:46,190 --> 01:14:48,647
因爲她想擺脫那筆錢。
Because she was trying to get rid of it.

1286
01:14:49,986 --> 01:14:52,443
在她從中偷走錢的同一家銀行裏？
In the same bank that she stole it from?

1287
01:14:52,530 --> 01:14:54,191
當然。
Certainly.

1288
01:14:54,281 --> 01:14:57,023
你看，她從來就不想要那錢。
You see, she never wanted the money in the first place.

1289
01:14:57,118 --> 01:14:59,860
- 她之所以拿走是因爲... - 爲什麼？
- She only took it because... - Because why?

1290
01:15:01,288 --> 01:15:03,529
因爲她控制不了自己。
Because she couldn't help herself.

1291
01:15:03,624 --> 01:15:05,364
呃，Elcott太太，我們感謝你的幫助，
Uh, we appreciate your help, Mrs. Elcott,

1292
01:15:05,459 --> 01:15:08,451
但你的理論是出於對嫌疑人的同情，
but your theory is based on sympathy for the suspect,

1293
01:15:08,546 --> 01:15:09,546
而不是事實。
not fact.

1294
01:15:09,630 --> 01:15:11,120
好了，女管理員。
Okay, matron.

1295
01:15:11,215 --> 01:15:12,580
不！
No!

1296
01:15:13,175 --> 01:15:14,585
好吧。
Alright.

1297
01:15:15,302 --> 01:15:18,044
你們想要供詞，我會確保你們得到一個。
You wanted a confession and I'll see that you get one.

1298
01:15:18,139 --> 01:15:20,801
非常感謝，但 Rose小姐不願意說話。
Thanks a lot, but miss Rose is not talking.

1299
01:15:20,891 --> 01:15:23,803
不是從 Rose小姐那裏，是從真正的搶劫犯那裏。
No, not from miss Rose, from the bank robber.

1300
01:15:23,894 --> 01:15:25,680
就是那個搶你們銀行的女人
From the woman who robbed your bank

1301
01:15:25,771 --> 01:15:28,683
戴着紅色假髮、穿黃色套裝逃走的那位。
and escaped in a red wig and a yellow suit.

1302
01:15:28,774 --> 01:15:29,889
我。
Me.

1303
01:15:31,944 --> 01:15:33,650
對不起，James。
I'm sorry, James.

1304
01:15:33,738 --> 01:15:36,821
改天我再解釋爲什麼非得選你們的銀行。
I'll just have to explain later why it had to be your bank.

1305
01:15:36,907 --> 01:15:38,772
但現在最重要的是
But right now, the most important thing

1306
01:15:38,868 --> 01:15:40,108
揪出事實真相
is to get to the truth of this

1307
01:15:40,202 --> 01:15:42,909
這樣這個可憐的無辜女孩就不必入獄。
so that this poor innocent girl doesn't have to go to jail.

1308
01:15:45,583 --> 01:15:47,790
所以請叫個速記員來吧，
So if you will call a stenographer

1309
01:15:47,877 --> 01:15:49,146
我會口述一份完整的陳述。
I will dictate a full statement.

1310
01:15:49,170 --> 01:15:51,582
現在，Elcott太太，我擔心你有些緊張過度。
Now, Mrs. Elcott, I'm afraid you're under a strain.

1311
01:15:51,672 --> 01:15:52,899
或許你最好把她送回家。
Perhaps you better take her home.

1312
01:15:52,923 --> 01:15:54,629
你知道，打個盹什麼的。
You know, a nap or somethin'.

1313
01:15:58,220 --> 01:16:00,552
你們不相信我嗎？
Why, you don't believe me.

1314
01:16:00,931 --> 01:16:02,387
你們任何人都不相信。
None of you.

1315
01:16:02,933 --> 01:16:05,925
當真相就擺在你面前時，你們都看不出來。
You don't recognize the truth when it slaps you in the face.

1316
01:16:09,648 --> 01:16:11,263
你覺得我瘋了嗎，不是嗎？
You think I'm crazy, don't you?

1317
01:16:11,358 --> 01:16:12,848
哦，不，當然不是。不是。
Oh, no, certainly not. No.

1318
01:16:12,943 --> 01:16:15,150
呃，你知道，有時候，呃……
Uh, you know, sometimes, uh...

1319
01:16:15,237 --> 01:16:17,102
嗯，我們有時都需要幫助。
Well, we all need help sometimes.

1320
01:16:18,365 --> 01:16:21,198
嗯，我並不處於緊張狀態。
Well, I am not under a strain.

1321
01:16:21,285 --> 01:16:23,116
至於我的頭腦，從來沒有
And as far as my head, it has never been

1322
01:16:23,204 --> 01:16:24,535
像此刻這般清晰。
clearer than at this moment.

1323
01:16:24,622 --> 01:16:26,362
至於我是否需要幫助，
And as far as my needing help is concerned,

1324
01:16:26,457 --> 01:16:29,870
讓我向你保證：我每週都見精神科醫生五次。
let me assure you that I see my psychiatrist five times a week.

1325
01:16:31,545 --> 01:16:32,876
女管理員。
Matron.

1326
01:16:33,464 --> 01:16:35,125
對不起，Rose小姐。
I'm sorry, miss Rose.

1327
01:16:35,216 --> 01:16:37,878
但別擔心，他們不會關你太久。
But don't worry, they can't keep you long.

1328
01:16:37,968 --> 01:16:40,175
我會讓他們相信我。我向你保證。
I'll make them believe me. I promise you.

1329
01:16:40,262 --> 01:16:41,672
謝謝。
Thank you.

1330
01:16:41,764 --> 01:16:43,925
但是——你知道嗎，Elcott太太，
But-but you know something, Mrs. Elcott,

1331
01:16:44,016 --> 01:16:45,972
呃——這真可惜，
a-and it's a shame,

1332
01:16:46,477 --> 01:16:48,513
就連我也不相信你。
even I don't believe you.

1333
01:16:59,406 --> 01:17:00,737
我可憐的寶貝。
My poor darling.

1334
01:17:00,825 --> 01:17:03,441
哦，James，我真失望。
Oh, I'm so disappointed in you, James.

1335
01:17:03,536 --> 01:17:05,276
你爲什麼不相信我？
Why won't you believe me?

1336
01:17:05,371 --> 01:17:07,987
相信你是竊盜癖患者？小偷？銀行劫匪？
Believe you're a kleptomaniac? A thief? A bank robber?

1337
01:17:08,082 --> 01:17:09,868
親愛的，你會那樣看我嗎？
Darling, would you believe that of me?

1338
01:17:09,959 --> 01:17:10,959
當然會。
Of course.

1339
01:17:11,043 --> 01:17:12,749
如果你真心想讓我相信你是小偷，我會相信的。
If you really and truly wanted me

1340
01:17:12,837 --> 01:17:14,748
to believe that you were a thief, I would.

1341
01:17:14,839 --> 01:17:17,171
- 因爲我信任你。 - 我怎麼能相信你？
- Because I trust you. - How can I believe you?

1342
01:17:17,258 --> 01:17:18,318
昨晚三點鐘
Last night at 3:00 in the morning

1343
01:17:18,342 --> 01:17:19,923
你還躺在我身旁。
you were in bed next to me.

1344
01:17:20,010 --> 01:17:22,501
那又有什麼問題？我們是夫妻。
Well, what's wrong with that? We're married.

1345
01:17:22,596 --> 01:17:25,008
嗯，但——那筆錢，親愛的。
Uh, but-but the money, darling.

1346
01:17:25,099 --> 01:17:26,635
哦，那件事。
Oh, that.

1347
01:17:26,725 --> 01:17:28,932
Gregory 替我把錢放回去了。
Gregory took it back for me.

1348
01:17:29,019 --> 01:17:31,351
我得說他做得並不怎麼好。
I must say he didn't do a very good job of it.

1349
01:17:31,438 --> 01:17:32,999
他並沒有在幫助你這件事上做得很好
He's not doing a very good job of helping you

1350
01:17:33,023 --> 01:17:35,685
通過遷就你這些幻想。
by humoring these fantasies of yours.

1351
01:17:35,776 --> 01:17:38,313
你知道 Gregory 爲什麼說我搶了你們銀行嗎？
Do you know why Gregory says I robbed your bank?

1352
01:17:38,404 --> 01:17:41,020
因爲你把更多注意力放在銀行上，而不是我身上。
Because you pay more attention to it than you do to me.

1353
01:17:42,491 --> 01:17:44,322
你幾乎都不再注意我了。
You hardly ever even notice me anymore.

1354
01:17:44,410 --> 01:17:46,947
我知道。我能做什麼？告訴我你想要什麼。
You know I do. What do you want? Tell me what you want.

1355
01:17:47,037 --> 01:17:49,403
任何事，任何你想要的，親愛的。
Anything, anything you want, darling.

1356
01:17:52,877 --> 01:17:55,038
好吧，真正讓我在意的只有一件事。
Well, there's only one thing I really care about.

1357
01:17:55,546 --> 01:17:57,787
那件事對我很重要。
Something that would mean a great deal to me.

1358
01:17:57,882 --> 01:17:58,962
說吧。
Name it.

1359
01:17:59,049 --> 01:18:00,710
我想舉辦一個體面的雞尾酒會
I'd like to give a nice cocktail party

1360
01:18:00,801 --> 01:18:02,291
爲你所有的朋友舉行。
for all of your friends.

1361
01:18:02,386 --> 01:18:04,047
一個雞尾酒會。
A cocktail party.

1362
01:18:06,682 --> 01:18:09,014
你要不要讓司機把你放在銀行門口？
Should you tell the driver to drop you off at the bank?

1363
01:18:09,101 --> 01:18:10,466
穿這身？
In this?

1364
01:18:34,335 --> 01:18:36,667
她在家嗎？Elcott 太太？
She's home? Mrs. Elcott?

1365
01:18:36,754 --> 01:18:38,915
請問誰打來？
Who is calling, please?

1366
01:18:39,673 --> 01:18:40,879
朋友。
Friends.

1367
01:18:42,134 --> 01:18:43,340
匿名的。
Anonymous.

1368
01:18:45,012 --> 01:18:47,424
匿名先生和太太。
Mr. and Mrs. anonymous.

1369
01:18:49,475 --> 01:18:50,715
你好。
Hello.

1370
01:18:51,810 --> 01:18:54,176
- 你記得 Sadaba 嗎？ - 還有 Ducky？
- You remember Sadaba? - And ducky?

1371
01:18:54,271 --> 01:18:55,727
當然記得。
Of course.

1372
01:18:56,357 --> 01:18:59,099
請坐，Elcott 太太。
Have a seat, Mrs. Elcott.

1373
01:19:01,779 --> 01:19:03,610
我有什麼能爲你效勞的嗎？
Is there something I can do for you?

1374
01:19:03,697 --> 01:19:07,155
- 爲我們？不。 - 我們要爲你做點事。
- For us? No. - We do something for you.

1375
01:19:07,243 --> 01:19:09,450
哦，我在等客人。
Oh, well, I'm expecting guests.

1376
01:19:09,536 --> 01:19:11,447
呃，如果你們是來賣衣服的...
Uh, if you're here to sell me a dress...

1377
01:19:11,538 --> 01:19:13,199
重要得多，不只是件衣服。
Much more important than a dress.

1378
01:19:13,290 --> 01:19:15,906
我們來賣給你自由。
We come to sell you freedom.

1379
01:19:16,835 --> 01:19:19,702
哦！那真是個了不起的事業。
Oh! Oh, well, that's a wonderful cause.

1380
01:19:19,797 --> 01:19:21,583
我一直對自由很感興趣。
I'm always interested in freedom.

1381
01:19:21,674 --> 01:19:24,131
- 爲所有人。 - 尤其是爲你。
- For everybody. - Especially for you.

1382
01:19:26,053 --> 01:19:27,714
現在說說錢。
The check now.

1383
01:19:28,764 --> 01:19:30,220
你想要多少？
How much would you like?

1384
01:19:30,307 --> 01:19:31,922
25000 美元。
Twenty-five thousand dollars.

1385
01:19:32,017 --> 01:19:34,053
要這麼多？
As much as that?

1386
01:19:34,144 --> 01:19:37,181
那是用來幹什麼的？
Well, what, uh, is it for?

1387
01:19:37,273 --> 01:19:39,855
爲了讓一位好女士不進監獄。
To keep a nice lady out of jail.

1388
01:19:39,942 --> 01:19:45,482
Sadaba 知道 Mrs. James Elcott 搶了她丈夫的銀行。
Sadaba knows Mrs. James Elcott robbed her husband's bank.

1389
01:19:50,244 --> 01:19:51,905
你知道這事？
You know that?

1390
01:19:52,496 --> 01:19:55,078
真的？你確定嗎？
Really? Are you positive?

1391
01:19:55,165 --> 01:19:57,156
你沒剛剛聽見她自己承認嗎？
You didn't hear her just tell you?

1392
01:19:58,335 --> 01:19:59,450
你能證明嗎？
Can you prove it?

1393
01:19:59,545 --> 01:20:02,878
Sadaba 是傻瓜嗎？
Is Sadaba a fool?

1394
01:20:02,965 --> 01:20:05,456
她當場就證明了。怎麼證明？
Certainly she proves it. How?

1395
01:20:07,720 --> 01:20:12,180
這是兩年前雜誌上的一張照片。
Here is a picture from magazine two years old.

1396
01:20:13,350 --> 01:20:14,931
你認出這位女士了嗎？
You recognize the lady?

1397
01:20:15,019 --> 01:20:17,431
- 是我！- 哦，別靠那麼近。
- It's me! - Oh, not so close.

1398
01:20:17,896 --> 01:20:21,184
Ducky，親愛的，讀上面的字。
Ducky, sweetheart, read the words.

1399
01:20:21,275 --> 01:20:24,312
“在慈善午宴上，紐約的 Mrs. James Elcott
"At luncheon for charity, Mrs. James Elcott of New York

1400
01:20:24,403 --> 01:20:29,067
身着 Givenchy 設計的黃色羊毛套裝。”
wearing a suit of yellow wool designed by Givenchy."

1401
01:20:29,158 --> 01:20:31,649
那就是穿黃色套裝的我！
It's me in the yellow suit!

1402
01:20:31,744 --> 01:20:34,030
如果有人看到了那...
Well, if anybody saw that...

1403
01:20:36,582 --> 01:20:38,664
你們在勒索我！
You're blackmailing me!

1404
01:20:39,043 --> 01:20:40,908
勒索是刑事犯罪。
Blackmail is a criminal offense.

1405
01:20:41,003 --> 01:20:42,743
我們的目的是
What we're trying to do

1406
01:20:42,838 --> 01:20:46,877
做一件價值 25000 美元的好事。
is a $25,000 good turn.

1407
01:20:46,967 --> 01:20:48,377
哦。
Oh.

1408
01:20:48,469 --> 01:20:51,302
如果我不付呢？
And suppose I won't pay it?

1409
01:20:51,388 --> 01:20:55,131
那你會付的，否則我們就把照片給你丈夫看。
But you will, or we show this to your husband.

1410
01:20:55,434 --> 01:20:57,971
哦，我能指望你們這麼做嗎？
Oh, can I depend on that?

1411
01:20:59,021 --> 01:21:00,511
算是我的承諾。
Here is my word.

1412
01:21:00,606 --> 01:21:03,643
她說的“指望”是什麼意思？
What does she mean, depend on it?

1413
01:21:03,734 --> 01:21:06,942
哦，他隨時會來。
Oh, he ought to be along any minute.

1414
01:21:07,029 --> 01:21:08,314
你能等嗎？
Can you wait?

1415
01:21:08,405 --> 01:21:12,648
也許丈夫也牽涉其中，是吧？
So maybe the husband is in the game, huh?

1416
01:21:12,743 --> 01:21:15,906
那我們甚至可以不用給他看？
So maybe we don't even bother to show him?

1417
01:21:15,996 --> 01:21:18,078
哦，你們一定要的，拜託。
Oh, you've got to, please.

1418
01:21:18,165 --> 01:21:20,406
我們沒有......
We don't got...

1419
01:21:20,501 --> 01:21:23,083
但也許我們應該把照片拿去給警察。
But maybe we take the picture to the police.

1420
01:21:23,170 --> 01:21:25,286
立刻。快點。
Right away. Quick.

1421
01:21:25,381 --> 01:21:27,372
你覺得怎麼樣？
What do you say to that?

1422
01:21:27,466 --> 01:21:29,297
好，我-我就跟你們去。
Okay, I-I'll go with you.

1423
01:21:29,385 --> 01:21:30,591
不。
No.

1424
01:21:30,677 --> 01:21:34,340
Ducky，這地方讓我覺得有點可疑。
Ducky, something is smelling crooked in the place.

1425
01:21:34,431 --> 01:21:37,423
- 出去。 - 不！哦，等等！拜託，聽我說！
- Out. - No! Oh, wait! Please, listen!

1426
01:21:37,518 --> 01:21:39,930
- 我們把證據處理掉！- 停下！你們在幹什麼？
- We get rid of the evidence! - Stop! What are you doing?

1427
01:21:40,020 --> 01:21:41,931
拜託，你們把一切都毀了！
Please, you're spoiling everything!

1428
01:21:42,022 --> 01:21:44,308
我們把證據吞了！吞下去！
We swallow the evidence! Swallow!

1429
01:21:44,400 --> 01:21:46,732
James，哦，親愛的。
James, oh, darling.

1430
01:21:46,819 --> 01:21:48,275
幸好你來了。
Thank heaven you're here.

1431
01:21:48,362 --> 01:21:52,401
親愛的，這是 Princess Sadaba 和 Ducky。
Darling, this is Princess Sadaba and Ducky.

1432
01:21:52,741 --> 01:21:55,699
他們來這裏是想勒索我。
And they came here to blackmail me.

1433
01:21:55,786 --> 01:21:59,620
Princess Sadaba，現在請向我丈夫解釋
Princess Sadaba, now please explain to my husband

1434
01:21:59,706 --> 01:22:02,072
爲什麼你要勒索我。
why you're blackmailing me.

1435
01:22:02,626 --> 01:22:06,665
我們是來給你太太看晚禮服的。
We came to interest your wife in an evening gown.

1436
01:22:06,755 --> 01:22:09,872
突然之間，居然有人跟我說起
Out of the blue, suddenly I'm hearing

1437
01:22:09,967 --> 01:22:11,548
呃，勒索的事。
uh, about blackmail.

1438
01:22:11,635 --> 01:22:13,500
James, 那不是真的
James, that's not true.

1439
01:22:13,595 --> 01:22:15,961
他們有確鑿的證據說我搶了你們的銀行。
They have positive proof that I robbed your bank.

1440
01:22:16,056 --> 01:22:17,056
什麼銀行？
What bank?

1441
01:22:17,141 --> 01:22:18,972
Mr. Elcott，很抱歉這麼說，
Mr. Elcott, I hate to say this,

1442
01:22:19,059 --> 01:22:21,641
但你娶了個有點古怪的女人。
but you are married to some wacky woman.

1443
01:22:21,728 --> 01:22:24,344
我妻子最近一直覺得不太好。
My wife has not been feeling too well lately.

1444
01:22:24,440 --> 01:22:28,058
James，你要相信他們還是相信我？
James, are you going to believe them or me?

1445
01:22:28,152 --> 01:22:29,983
親愛的，你又在幻想了。
Honey, you're imagining things again.

1446
01:22:30,070 --> 01:22:33,312
幻想？幻想？
Imagining things? Imagining things?

1447
01:22:33,407 --> 01:22:36,114
好吧，問他他在吃什麼。
Alright, ask him what he's eating.

1448
01:22:37,870 --> 01:22:39,986
打擾一下，先生，你在吃什麼？
Excuse me, sir, what are you eating?

1449
01:22:41,081 --> 01:22:44,073
- 我吃得晚了。 - 謝謝。
- I had a late lunch. - Thank you.

1450
01:22:45,586 --> 01:22:47,076
哦！
Oh!

1451
01:22:49,465 --> 01:22:51,126
來吧，殿下。
Come, highness.

1452
01:22:54,261 --> 01:22:55,592
對不起。
I'm sorry.

1453
01:22:55,679 --> 01:22:57,761
如果我能彌補什麼的話……
If there's any way I can make amends...

1454
01:22:59,099 --> 01:23:01,010
你有沒有氣泡水之類的？
You got maybe a little seltzer?

1455
01:23:01,101 --> 01:23:02,557
出去！
Out!

1456
01:23:11,570 --> 01:23:14,528
James，多麼有趣的聚會啊。
James, such a fun party.

1457
01:23:14,615 --> 01:23:16,606
你的Penelope什麼時候出來？
When's your Penelope going to appear?

1458
01:23:16,700 --> 01:23:18,900
也許她拉鍊卡住了。我去看看。
Maybe she's having zipper trouble. I'll just go and see.

1459
01:23:21,371 --> 01:23:23,032
Mannix 醫生。
Dr. Mannix.

1460
01:23:25,250 --> 01:23:27,787
我不知道精神病醫生會上門看病。
I didn't know a psychiatrist made house calls.

1461
01:23:27,878 --> 01:23:29,493
我是個客人。
I am a guest.

1462
01:23:29,588 --> 01:23:31,749
我還有請柬，看到了嗎？
And I have an invitation. See?

1463
01:23:31,840 --> 01:23:33,751
你有過。現在沒有了。
You did. Now you don't.

1464
01:23:34,176 --> 01:23:35,837
那不是挺孩子氣的做法嗎？
Isn't that a rather childish thing to do?

1465
01:23:35,928 --> 01:23:37,543
那來點更成熟的怎麼樣？
Then how about something more grownup?

1466
01:23:37,638 --> 01:23:39,299
比如，給你一拳鼻子怎麼樣？
Say, a punch in the nose?

1467
01:23:39,389 --> 01:23:42,256
把你身上的怒氣發泄到我身上對你沒用。
Taking out your aggressions on me is not going to help you.

1468
01:23:42,351 --> 01:23:44,511
對你沒用，但你也幫不了我妻子。
It won't help you, but then you're not helping my wife.

1469
01:23:44,561 --> 01:23:46,893
我只負責這案子三年，先生。
I've only been on the case for three years, sir.

1470
01:23:46,980 --> 01:23:49,392
到這段時間結束時，你的病人，你以前的病人
At the end of which time, your patient, your former patient

1471
01:23:49,483 --> 01:23:51,127
比起開始時更糟了。
is worse off than when she first started with you.

1472
01:23:51,151 --> 01:23:53,688
以前的？你說以前的是什麼意思？我不明白。
Former? W-W-What do you mean by, uh, former? I don't understand.

1473
01:23:53,779 --> 01:23:55,269
那我來解釋。你被解僱了。
Then I'll explain. You're fired.

1474
01:23:55,364 --> 01:23:57,730
等等！Elcott，你不能那樣！
Wait! Elcott, you can't do that!

1475
01:24:05,374 --> 01:24:07,535
Penny。Penny？
Penny. Penny?

1476
01:24:07,626 --> 01:24:09,287
嗯，有事嗎？
Yes, what is it?

1477
01:24:09,753 --> 01:24:12,039
大家都在找你，親愛的。你要出來嗎？
Everyone's asking for you, honey. Are you coming out?

1478
01:24:12,130 --> 01:24:14,166
我告訴過你，要的。
I told you, yes.

1479
01:24:14,258 --> 01:24:15,464
什麼時候？
When?

1480
01:24:16,718 --> 01:24:19,334
等Mildred Halliday來了我就出來。
As soon as Mildred Halliday gets here.

1481
01:24:19,429 --> 01:24:21,715
Mildred Halliday和這有什麼關係？
What's Mildred Halliday got to do with it?

1482
01:24:23,809 --> 01:24:25,140
你會看到的。
You'll see.

1483
01:24:26,687 --> 01:24:29,929
Penny，讓我進去我們談談，好嗎？
Penny, just let me in and we'll talk it over, huh?

1484
01:24:31,441 --> 01:24:33,227
Penny，如果你能回答我就好了。
Penny, if you'll just answer me.

1485
01:24:33,318 --> 01:24:34,933
Penny，開門！
Penny, open!

1486
01:24:36,738 --> 01:24:38,319
這個門把有點卡。哦。
This knob, it sticks. Oh.

1487
01:24:38,407 --> 01:24:39,842
- 我得找個螺絲刀。- 嗯哼。
- I have to get a screwdriver. - Mm-hmm.

1488
01:24:39,866 --> 01:24:42,448
你應該在黃頁裏找找。
Well, you should try to find it in the yellow pages.

1489
01:24:42,536 --> 01:24:44,447
或者打開我的門。
Or open my door.

1490
01:24:46,790 --> 01:24:48,951
你好，Mildred。歡迎來參加聚會。
Hello, Mildred. Welcome to the party.

1491
01:24:54,047 --> 01:24:57,756
哦，James，確保Mildred得到她想要的一切。
Oh, James, make sure Mildred gets everything she wants.

1492
01:25:00,804 --> 01:25:03,386
- 哦，可憐的親愛的。- 哦，Mildred。
- Oh, poor darling. - Oh, Mildred.

1493
01:25:03,473 --> 01:25:04,883
你能幫我一個忙嗎？
Would you mind doing me a favor?

1494
01:25:04,975 --> 01:25:06,761
哦，任何事，任何事。
Oh, anything, anything.

1495
01:25:06,852 --> 01:25:08,888
試着換個人親一下，行嗎？
Try kissing somebody else for a change, huh?

1496
01:25:08,979 --> 01:25:10,014
說真的，我確實有親，
