1544
01:29:10,554 --> 01:29:13,045
我不怕你，你這個大惡霸。
I'm not afraid of you, you big bully.

1545
01:29:13,139 --> 01:29:16,131
一個老太太拿走...（這個主意）
The idea of an old woman taking a...

