Thank you.

1550
01:29:48,508 --> 01:29:53,298
啊，我的可育雞蛋和酸奶。我要告你。
Oh, my fertile eggs and my yogurt. I'll sue you.

1551
01:29:53,388 --> 01:29:57,347
