Now let's see who's under this ridiculous-looking mask.

1552
01:30:00,020 --> 01:30:02,136
她給我十塊錢的時候可沒提過要捏鼻子這事。
She didn't say nothin' about nose-tweaking

1553
01:30:02,230 --> 01:30:03,686
她給我十塊錢的時候可沒提過。
when she give me the ten bucks.

1554
01:30:03,773 --> 01:30:05,604
她？誰？
