1555
01:30:05,692 --> 01:30:08,980
她說是個惡作劇，我信了她。
A practical joke, she said, and I believed her.

1556
01:30:09,070 --> 01:30:12,187
她那雙又大又悲傷的褐色眼睛，
Her with those big, sad brown eyes,

1557
01:30:12,282 --> 01:30:14,819
