1572
01:31:06,336 --> 01:31:07,826
她，她，她往哪邊走了？
Which, which-which way did she go?

1573
01:31:07,921 --> 01:31:09,411
往市區方向。
Downtown.

1574
01:31:14,344 --> 01:31:15,834
往市區？
Downtown?

1575
01:31:18,014 --> 01:31:19,754
你盯着什麼看，Mac？
What you starin' at, Mac?

1576
01:31:21,101 --> 01:31:22,386
那張臉。
That face.

1577
01:31:25,480 --> 01:31:29,098
哦，剛纔那一刻，你看起來就像我太太。
Oh, for-for a moment, you looked just like my wife.

1578
01:31:30,360 --> 01:31:32,601
我還以爲我娶的是條狗。
And I thought mine was a dog.

1579
01:31:34,572 --> 01:31:36,028
你說往市區？
Downtown, you said?

1580
01:31:36,366 --> 01:31:38,982
呃，帶我去中心街，警察局總部。
Uh, take me to centre street, police headquarters.

1581
01:31:41,788 --> 01:31:43,198
Penelope？
Penelope?

1582
01:31:44,374 --> 01:31:46,490
我說得對。你來找我了。
I was right. You came to me.

1583
01:31:46,584 --> 01:31:47,824
我還能去找誰？
Who else would I come to?

1584
01:31:47,919 --> 01:31:49,063
你要我先走嗎，不等你？
You want me to go ahead without you?

1585
01:31:49,087 --> 01:31:50,668
聽着，你不會相信的，
Listen, you're not gonna believe this,

1586
01:31:50,755 --> 01:31:53,041
可有人剛搶了你丈夫的銀行。
but somebody just knocked over your husband's bank.

1587
01:31:53,133 --> 01:31:55,920
嗯，你可能不信，但我信你。
Well, you won't believe this, but I believe you.

1588
01:31:57,762 --> 01:31:59,718
你搶了你丈夫的銀行？
You robbed your husband's bank?

1589
01:31:59,806 --> 01:32:00,921
不止一次。兩次。
Twice.

1590
01:32:05,729 --> 01:32:09,813
中士，我剛破了 Elcott 案。
Sergeant, I just solved the Elcott case.

1591
01:32:10,692 --> 01:32:13,775
長大後我想當個像你這樣的警察。
When I grow up, I wanna be a cop just like you.

1592
01:32:14,529 --> 01:32:16,465
你現在得放了 Honeysuckle，是吧？
You'll have to release honeysuckle now, won't you?

1593
01:32:16,489 --> 01:32:18,150
以童子軍的名譽發誓。
Scout's honor.

1594
01:32:19,617 --> 01:32:21,824
我來了，我來了。
I'm going, I'm going.

1595
01:32:23,872 --> 01:32:29,117
嗯，我想我們可能不會再見面了。
Well, I, uh, I guess we won't be seeing one another anymore.

1596
01:32:29,210 --> 01:32:30,620
你們不會要逮捕我嗎？
Aren't you gonna arrest me?

1597
01:32:30,712 --> 01:32:32,828
除非銀行行長提出起訴，
Not unless the bank president presses charges,

1598
01:32:32,922 --> 01:32:34,537
否則幾乎不太可能。
which is hardly likely.

1599
01:32:36,051 --> 01:32:37,712
謝謝你，Horatio。
Thank you, Horatio.

1600
01:32:38,845 --> 01:32:40,301
不客氣，Penelope。
You're welcome, Penelope.

1601
01:32:43,183 --> 01:32:45,845
好吧，這段犯罪生涯雖短，但很精彩。
Well, it was a great criminal career while it lasted.

1602
01:32:54,402 --> 01:32:56,563
算是最棒的之一。
One of the best.

1603
01:33:18,426 --> 01:33:20,633
Elcott 先生，進來吧。
Mr. Elcott, come on in.

1604
01:33:26,726 --> 01:33:28,933
