I was crying like anything.

1633
01:34:47,515 --> 01:34:48,721
你不明白嗎？
Don't you get it?

1634
01:34:48,808 --> 01:34:51,390
看，偷東西不再讓我開心了。
You see, the stealing didn't make me cheerful anymore.

1635
01:34:51,477 --> 01:34:52,717
