and you'd probably have difficulty

1647
01:35:16,085 --> 01:35:18,076
把我從父親般的角色調整爲情人形象。
readjusting me from a father figure

1648
01:35:18,171 --> 01:35:19,627
把我從父親形象調整爲情人形象。
to a lover image.

1649
01:35:20,423 --> 01:35:22,539
