And I'm probably too tall for you.

1650
01:35:22,634 --> 01:35:24,170
太老了。
Too old.

1651
01:35:24,260 --> 01:35:26,000
我敢肯定你沒有足夠的壁櫥空間
I'm sure you don't have enough closet space

1652
01:35:26,095 --> 01:35:27,960
給我的衣服放在你公寓裏。
for my clothes in your apartment.

1653
01:35:28,389 --> 01:35:30,254
我會打呼嚕，而且...
I do snore a lot and...

1654
01:35:31,851 --> 01:35:34,058
我有胃潰瘍。
I have this ulcer.

1655
01:35:37,106 --> 01:35:39,597
Dr. Knoblock！
Dr. Knoblock!

1656
01:35:41,194 --> 01:35:42,855
我需要幫助！
I need help!

1657
01:35:44,572 --> 01:35:46,052
Penelope，你怎麼能這樣對我？
How could you do this to me, Penelope?

1658
01:35:46,115 --> 01:35:49,107
你知道我受不了被拒絕。
You know I can't stand rejection.

1659
01:35:57,210 --> 01:35:58,620
Penelope。
Penelope.

1660
01:36:00,213 --> 01:36:01,874
Mannix 醫生。
Dr. Mannix.

1661
01:36:03,216 --> 01:36:05,878
呃，你，你得幫我。
Uh, you, you've got to help me.

1662
01:36:05,969 --> 01:36:09,382
我看哪裏，眼裏全是 Penelope。
Everywhere I look, all I can see is Penelope.

1663
01:36:09,472 --> 01:36:12,179
在銀行、出租車上、在警察局。
In the bank, in the cab, at the police station.

1664
01:36:12,267 --> 01:36:13,387
就在剛纔我進來時，
And just now when I came in,

1665
01:36:13,476 --> 01:36:15,637
連你在我眼裏也像 Penelope。
even you looked like Penelope to me.

1666
01:36:15,728 --> 01:36:18,060
我知道這一切都和愛她、想念她混在一起
I know it's all mixed up with loving her and missing her

1667
01:36:18,147 --> 01:36:20,058
還有，那種內疚感
and, and feeling guilty

1668
01:36:20,149 --> 01:36:23,186
因爲那家愚蠢的銀行而把她擠到一邊。
about shoving her aside for that stupid bank.

1669
01:36:24,612 --> 01:36:26,898
我可能不該把這些無聊事說給你聽。
I probably shouldn't be boring you with all this.

1670
01:36:26,990 --> 01:36:28,355
哦，不，別停下來。
Oh, no, don't stop now.

1671
01:36:28,449 --> 01:36:30,405
你正說到精彩部分。
You're just getting to the good part.

1672
01:36:30,493 --> 01:36:32,905
啊，現在我真的迷失了。
Ah, now I'm really gone.

1673
01:36:32,996 --> 01:36:34,987
你甚至聽起來像她。
You even sound like her.

1674
01:36:35,081 --> 01:36:38,244
要是有什麼辦法，要是我能找到她
If there was only some way, if I could only find her

1675
01:36:38,334 --> 01:36:40,825
告訴她我有多需要她。
and tell her how much I need her.

1676
01:36:49,637 --> 01:36:51,343
Mannix 醫生，你需要幫助。
Dr. Mannix, you need help.

1677
01:36:51,431 --> 01:36:52,825
現在大家都需要。
Everybody does these days.

1678
01:36:52,849 --> 01:36:54,326
唯一不同的是，我們這些適應得較好的人
The only difference is, we well-adjusted

1679
01:36:54,350 --> 01:36:56,591
還能及時意識到。
maladjusted ones realize it in time.

1680
01:36:58,313 --> 01:37:00,474
而且，最好的幫助
And besides, the best help of all

1681
01:37:00,565 --> 01:37:02,476
就是在家裏才能得到的那種幫助。
is the kind you can only get at home.

1682
01:37:14,787 --> 01:37:16,698
忘記鞋子意味着什麼？
What does it mean when you forget your shoes?

1683
01:37:16,789 --> 01:37:19,326
- 嗯... - 這意味着我們都治好了，親愛的。
- Well... - It means we're cured, darling.

1684
01:37:32,513 --> 01:37:39,055
